OL,6,FA Nottingham care home has been placed
OL,7,Finto special measures after residents
OL,8,Fwere found to have been neglected by
OL,9,Fstaff.
OL,11,FBraywood Gardens, in Carlton,
OL,12,FNottingham, has been rated inadequate
OL,13,Fby the Care Quality Commission (CQC),
OL,14,Fand has been prevented from admitting
OL,15,Fnew residents without CQC's
OL,16,Fpermission, following an inspection
OL,17,Fcarried out in May.
