OL,3,CCare home placed in special measures
OL,4,Cafter 'at risk' residents neglected
OL,6,FAt the time of the inspection, there
OL,7,Fwere 88 people living in the home,
OL,8,Fwhich is operated by Runwood Homes
OL,9,FLimited, and provides accommodation
OL,10,Fand personal care to older people,
OL,11,Fsome of whom are living with dementia.
OL,13,FThe inspection was carried out after
OL,14,Fpeople raised concerns about patient
OL,15,Fsafety at the home.
OL,17,FThe CQC report highlights a lack of
OL,18,Fstrong leadership, and low staff
OL,19,Fnumbers which contributed to issues
OL,20,Faround patient safety.
