OL,3,CCare home placed in special measures
OL,4,Cafter 'at risk' residents neglected
OL,6,F"We heard people often having to shout
OL,7,Ffor staff to support them which didn't
OL,8,Falways happen.
OL,10,F"One person told us they had
OL,11,Fcomplained that staff weren't quick
OL,12,Fenough when they needed support to use
OL,13,Fthe toilet.
OL,15,F"The staff member responded by telling
OL,16,Fthem to use their incontinence pad and
OL,17,Fthey would have to wait in their used
OL,18,Fpad until the morning when staff could
OL,19,Fsupport them. This shows staff didn't
OL,20,Falways treat people with kindness or
OL,21,Fdignity."
