OL,6,FResidents also told inspectors that
OL,7,Fthey were worried about their safety,
OL,8,Fwith altercations between residents
OL,9,Fnot referred to the local authority
OL,10,Fsafeguarding team.
OL,12,FInspectors also found:
OL,14,FFollowing the inspection, Braywood
OL,15,FGardens' overall rating has dropped
OL,16,Ffrom requires improvement to
OL,17,Finadequate. Its ratings for being
OL,18,Feffective and caring dropped from good
OL,19,Fto inadequate.
