OL,6,FThe home maintained its requires
OL,7,Fimprovement rating for being safe and
OL,8,Fwell-led, and its good rating for
OL,9,Fresponse.
OL,11,FThe CQC has placed conditions on the
OL,12,Fservice to prevent more people from
OL,13,Fbeing admitted without regulators'
OL,14,Fpermission, until significant
OL,15,Fimprovements have been made.
OL,17,FThe service will be kept under close
OL,18,Freview, and the CQC says further
OL,19,Faction will be taken if it does not
OL,20,Fsee rapid and widespread improvement.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
