OL,6,FA spokesperson for Braywood Gardens
OL,7,Fsaid: "We can confirm that an
OL,8,Fimmediate and robust action plan was
OL,9,Fput in place following the inspection
OL,10,Fundertaken by CQC.
OL,12,F"These findings were also identified
OL,13,Fby the provider and a managerial
OL,14,Fchange was made which has instantly
OL,15,Fbrought the service back to the high
OL,16,Fstandard we have seen previously at
OL,17,FBraywood Gardens.
