OL,6,F"Co-working with Nottingham County
OL,7,FCouncil (NCC) has been very productive
OL,8,Fand they too recognise the service is
OL,9,Fnow providing the high level of care
OL,10,Fformerly seen.
OL,12,F"We are actively encouraging a return
OL,13,Finspection visit from CQC where we
OL,14,Fexpect the service to return to an
OL,15,Foverall Good rating.
