OL,6,F"We take on board all findings raised
OL,7,Fby CQC and have worked tirelessly to
OL,8,Finstantly put these areas right. We
OL,9,Fare pleased to say the home is now in
OL,10,Fa very good position with exceptional
OL,11,Fleadership and staff.
OL,13,F"We thank our staff and the home
OL,14,Fmanager for their efficient and
OL,15,Fprofessional response to see the
OL,16,Fservice back to the expected standard
OL,17,Fand will work with all key
OL,18,Fstakeholders to see this maintained"
